### Prerequisites:

- Before requesting a device addition, please ensure there is not already a request for the device among the open issues.
- Make sure your Homey is upgraded to firmware v5 or higher.
- You need a physical example of the device.

### Device Information

- Device Name: `SmarterCurry Solar Lux Sensor`
- Device Model: `TS0601`
- Device Description: `Solar-powered Zigbee light/lux sensor with dusk detection. Manufacturer: _TZE284_aaeasoll`
- Link to device image: https://currysmarter.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/%E5%85%89%E6%84%9F.jpg
- Link to product page: https://currysmarter.com/product/tuya-zigbee-lichtsensor/?v=5f02f0889301

